        <h3 class="subheading">The Cubby Hole Scale Model Group</h3>
        <p>The Cubby started off in 2017 as a facebook community page, comprising of well over 300 scale modellers from around the world. The backgrounds and reasons for their interest in scale modelling ranged greatly, and many a varied approach and discussion was had. The success of this group inspired the founder, Lee Hayward, to expand his passion for scale model building, and start a related business.</p>
